    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sudden occurrences of violent expansion or bursting, intentional or accidental, caused by rapidly-developed internal energy, as by chemical or nuclear reaction, or esape of gases or vapors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
